structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
ISSUANCE OF BONDS AND CONTROL OF FUNDS

law.catch_line: KRS 66.310 not applicable to appropriations under KRS 66.520.
law.text: The provisions of KRS 66.310 shall apply neither to fiscal court appropriations made to the board under KRS 66.520 nor to the board's budget or operations.
